snippet.title: Jenny LeClue - Detectivu Release Date Trailer - Steam, GOG, Apple Arcade
snippet.description:
Jenny LeClue - Detectivu is a thrilling mystery adventure game about detectiving, friendship, and choosiness.

Coming September 19th to Steam and GOG. Coming to Apple Arcade super soon!
Wishlist https://store.steampowered.com/app/319870/Jenny_LeClue__Detectivu/

Coming to Nintendo Switch and PS4 later this year.
